\pard\pardeftab720\sl400\sa140\ql\qnatural

\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 Place the simple syrup, mascarpone cheese, limoncello, and salt in a {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/food-processor/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 food processor}}. Process until the mixture is smooth. Pour the mixture into an 8-by-8-inch glass {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/cookware-and-bakeware-materials/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 baking dish}}. Freeze for at least 4 hours or until the mixture is firm.\
Using the tines of a fork, scrape the mixture into small serving bowls or glasses. Serve immediately
